Ibu, di mana kau?

00:26:28.160 --> 00:26:28.920
Ibu!

00:26:29.519 --> 00:26:30.759
Aku takut...

00:27:14.720 --> 00:27:15.519
Ibu?

00:27:25.799 --> 00:27:26.599
Ibu?

00:27:30.200 --> 00:27:31.720
Ibu, di mana kau?

